# AI Elements Vue

AI Elements Vue is a component library built on top of shadcn-vue to help you build AI-native applications faster.[Documentation](https://www.ai-elements-vue.com/overview/introduction) [GitHub](https://github.com/vuepont/ai-elements-vue)

[**Shadcn Vue**\\
\\
Our AI Elements are built on Shadcn Vue's foundation, leveraging its design system to create specialized AI-native components with modern UI patterns.](https://www.shadcn-vue.com/)

[**Tailwind CSS**\\
\\
Tailwind CSS powers our styling system, enabling rapid development of AI-focused interfaces with utility-first classes for customizable, maintainable components.](https://tailwindcss.com/)

[**TypeScript**\\
\\
TypeScript provides type safety and developer experience for our AI Elements library, ensuring reliable APIs and better IntelliSense support.](https://www.typescriptlang.org/)
